docs.text: Welcome to MkDocs For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. def main(name: str = "RsR"): print(name) a link to the next page Link to next page NEXT Link to 3rd PAGE 3rd page LINK LOCAL TEST 3rd PAGE
